  <brief_title>OC000459 Dose Finding Study in Patients With Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose Finding Study in Patients With Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthma: A Parallel Group, Randomised, Placebo Controlled, Double Blind Assessment of Oral Oc000459 Dosed At Three Dose Schedules for Twelve Weeks Finding Study In Patients With Mild To Moderate Persistent Asthma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
